We had to chase minions of out this base, then we had a visit from
Maurader.  They must be up to something.&quot;

Lord Perseus followed them to the cell which was located in the lower base
near the power room; but he stayed to the side so the prisoner wouldn&#39;t
overhear the conversation.

Meanwhile...

As the Maximal team, lead by Salveo, began organizing the storage room, they
came across a stack of metal in the corner.  Apparently to the last maximal
team, these were the &quot;broken&quot; doors; however with the base in the state it
was in now, the discovery of these doors was this was some of the best news
they had all day.  They immediately carted the doors out of the room and
began mounting a set of replacement doors onto the front entrance of the
base.

